{"id":657929,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2020/10/【图说天朝】最后一段令人猝不及防/","date":"2020-10-17T05:14:12Z","modified":"2020-10-17T05:14:12Z","title":"【图说天朝】最后一段令人猝不及防","content":"<p>10月13日，一名青岛的微博博主写下了她的核酸检测见闻：一位拾荒大爷因担心检测需要付费而一度犹豫，原本以为这是一个反映社会沉重现实的文字，未料博主最后一段笔锋一转，成为了“爱国文字”，令网友感到猝不及防。</p>\n<blockquote><p>@big_ear_cat：最后一段突然阐明中心思想，我有点猝不及防，主要是脱离墙国语文课太久了。</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-657818\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/10/EkSi71lXkAE7VgQ.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"233\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/10/EkSi71lXkAE7VgQ.jpeg 1199w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/10/EkSi71lXkAE7VgQ-300x140.jpeg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/10/EkSi71lXkAE7VgQ-1024x477.jpeg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/10/EkSi71lXkAE7VgQ-768x358.jpeg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/10/EkSi71lXkAE7VgQ-1080x504.jpeg 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n</blockquote>\n","author":1069,"categories":[18271,41492,38912,39486],"tags":[40204,39929,25859]}